snippet.title: Shadow of the Tomb Raider - The Pillar [ESRB]
snippet.description:
Discover the truth behind the legend of the Maya apocalypse in The Pillar, now available! To reclaim an ancient treasure, Lara Croft must defy the treacherous storms of an all-new challenge tomb, all while fighting Trinity. Brave the storm: https://tombraider.games/tombr66ec1

Subscribe to our channel to keep up-to-date with all things Tomb Raider and Lara Croft: https://www.youtube.com/user/tombraider?sub_confirmation=1
